'''''Super Bowl Sunday''''' is a 1985 video game published by [[The Avalon Hill Game Company]].

==Gameplay==
''Super Bowl Sunday'' is a game in which [[American football]] is simulated in a strategy game based on statistics.<ref name="CGW42"/>

==Reception==
Wyatt Lee reviewed the game for ''[[Computer Gaming World]]'', and wrote that "the game is worth playing and offers realistic results."<ref name="CGW42">{{cite magazine |last=Lee |first=Wyatt |title=The Electronic Gridiron |magazine=Computer Gaming World |date=December 1987 |volume=1 |issue=42 |pages=42}}</ref>

